# 🚦 Smart City Interactive Power BI Dashboard

This is a comprehensive **Power BI dashboard project** designed to analyze key urban metrics for smart city development — from **air quality** to **transportation trends** and **public safety** indicators.

---

## 📊 Dashboard Overview

The report contains **3 fully dynamic pages**, each offering unique insights:

### 🟩 Page 1 – City Overview Dashboard
- City-wise AQI comparison (Map + Column Chart)
- Total Accidents, Vehicles, and Pollution Levels (KPI Cards)
- Transport usage by mode (Donut chart)
- Filters for city & year (dropdown slicers)

### 🟨 Page 2 – Pollution Analysis
- AQI trend over time (Line chart)
- Pollution Source breakdown (Pie chart)
- AQI category per city (Table with DAX classification)

### 🟦 Page 3 – Transport & Traffic Analysis
- Usage by transport mode over years (Stacked column chart)
- Vehicle count trend (Line chart)
- *Ribbon chart* showing top accident-prone cities over time
- *Decomposition tree* exploring usage by year → city → mode
- Tree map showing transport usage share

---

## 🔁 Features

- ✅ Fully interactive with slicers, cross-filtering & bookmarks  
- ✅ DAX-powered measures for dynamic KPIs and title updates  
- ✅ Drill-through to city-level detail pages  
- ✅ Tooltip-based mini charts (for hover-based insights)  
- ✅ Responsive design for web & mobile view  

---

## 🧠 Built With

- Power BI Desktop  
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)  
- Power Query for data cleaning  
- Smart layout design with advanced visuals  
- CSV data 

